# Public model assets: only the redistributable base is committed (ADR-0003) —
# the detector (MIT lineage) + both arch manifests (repo-generated metadata).
# The landmark + embedder safetensors have no upstream LICENSE, so they are
# never committed or deployed; the Pages demo collects them via a drop-zone.
